# Live Launchpad — clean URL aliases (Netlify _redirects)
# Additive only: the real .html files are still served directly, so every
# existing /<page>.html link keeps working. These 301s give stable, rename-proof
# URLs for the 5-destination IA — if a file is renamed later, update only the
# target here and external links survive.

/schedule      /schedule.html            301
/calendar      /calendar.html            301
/watch         /watch.html               301
/news          /news.html                301
/arcade        /games.html               301
/quiz          /play.html                301
/learn         /learn-hub.html           301
/rockets       /explorer.html            301
/rocket-database  /rocket-db.html        301
/reliability   /index-reliability.html   301
/in-dev        /development.html         301
/about         /about.html               301
